<section id="contacto">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="contact-card">
      <h2>Hablemos de tu proyecto</h2>
      <p class="contact-copy">
        Cuéntame qué necesitas y conversemos, sin costo, sobre cómo la IA y una ingeniería
        sólida pueden acelerar tu próximo proyecto de software.
      </p>
      <div class="contact-links">
        <a class="contact-link" href="mailto:pablo.cornejo.v@gmail.com">
          <span class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="label-main">pablo.cornejo.v@gmail.com</span>
        </a>
        <a class="contact-link" href="https://wa.me/56957591164" target="_blank" rel="noopener">
          <span class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="label-main">+56 9 5759 1164 <span class="label-sub">WhatsApp</span></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">(se abre en una nueva pestaña)</span>
        </a>
        <a
          class="contact-link"
          href="https://www.linkedin.com/in/pablo-cornejo-villarroel-43973a59/"
          target="_blank"
          rel="noopener"
        >
          <span class="icon-dot" aria-hidden="true"></span>
          <span class="label-main">LinkedIn <span class="label-sub">Pablo Cornejo Villarroel</span></span>
          <span class="visually-hidden">(se abre en una nueva pestaña)</span>
        </a>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<style>
  .contact-card {
    max-width: 720px;
    margin: 0 auto;
    background: var(--bg-surface);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-top: 3px solid transparent;
    border-image: var(--gradient-ai) 1;
    border-radius: var(--radius-lg);
    padding: clamp(var(--space-6), 5vw, var(--space-7));
    text-align: center;
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-4);
  }

  .contact-card p.contact-copy {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    max-width: 480px;
  }

  .contact-links {
    display: flex;
    flex-direction: column;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    width: 100%;
    max-width: 380px;
    margin-top: var(--space-3);
  }

  .contact-link {
    display: flex;
    align-items: center;
    gap: var(--space-3);
    justify-content: center;
    background: var(--bg-elevated);
    border: 1px solid var(--border-subtle);
    border-radius: var(--radius-sm);
    padding: var(--space-4) var(--space-5);
    font-weight: 500;
    font-size: 0.95rem;
    transition:
      border-color 0.2s ease,
      transform 0.15s ease,
      background 0.2s ease;
  }

  .contact-link:hover,
  .contact-link:focus-visible {
    border-color: rgba(34, 211, 238, 0.45);
    transform: translateY(-2px);
    background: var(--bg-surface);
  }

  .contact-link .icon-dot {
    width: 8px;
    height: 8px;
    border-radius: 50%;
    background: var(--gradient-ai);
    flex-shrink: 0;
  }

  .contact-link .label-main {
    overflow-wrap: break-word;
    min-width: 0;
  }

  .contact-link .label-sub {
    color: var(--text-secondary);
    font-size: 0.8125rem;
    font-weight: 400;
    margin-left: var(--space-1);
  }

  @media (min-width: 641px) {
    .contact-links {
      flex-direction: row;
      max-width: none;
      align-items: stretch;
    }

    .contact-link {
      flex: 1;
      min-width: 0;
    }
  }
</style>
